OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day with plenty
OL,6,Fof sunshine and feeling warm or very
OL,7,Fwarm. Cloudier with a little rain
OL,8,Fearly in the evening across northern
OL,9,FPerthshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry, sunny and warm evening
OL,12,Ffor most, but perhaps more in the way
OL,13,Fof cloud across northern Perthshire.
OL,14,FDry for the rest of the night with
OL,15,Fclear spells.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FDry with a good deal of warm
OL,18,Fsunshine. However more in the way of
OL,19,Fcloud around eastern coasts where it
OL,20,Fwill feel cooler than Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
