OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and bright with a good deal of
OL,7,Fsunshine. Warm inland, but cooler
OL,8,Falong the east coast on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
